Question: What is the smiling woman to the right of the glasses doing, waiting or staring?

Reference Answer: staring

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n470920.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='RIGHT')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='glasses')
IMAGE1=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='woman')
IMAGE2=CROP(image=IMAGE1,box=BOX2)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE2,question='Is the woman smiling?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE2,question='Is the woman waiting?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE2,question='Is the woman staring?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'waiting' if {ANSWER1} and not {ANSWER0} and not {ANSWER2} else'staring' if {ANSWER2} and not {ANSWER0} and not {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
